headline: Jack Henry Celebrates its Successful Collaboration with Corpay for International Wires
summary: Jack Henry (Nasdaq: JKHY) is pleased to recognize the success of its collaboration with Corpay, Inc.'s* (NYSE: CPAY) Cross-Border Solutions business to provide international wires for its clients.
